    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>总结下mysql的排行榜查询，需求是对当日销售业绩额排序。</p><hr><p>测试数据如下：</p><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">CREATE TABLE `t_sale_rank`  (</span><br><span class="line">  `id` int(<span class="number">11</span>) NOT NULL,</span><br><span class="line">  `emp_no` varchar(<span class="number">10</span>) CHARACTER <span class="built_in">SET</span> utf8 COLLATE utf8_general_ci NULL DEFAULT NULL COMMENT <span class="string">&#x27;员工编号&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">  `sale_amt` decimal(<span class="number">19</span>, <span class="number">2</span>) NULL DEFAULT NULL COMMENT <span class="string">&#x27;销售额&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">  `create_time` datetime(<span class="number">0</span>) NULL DEFAULT NULL COMMENT <span class="string">&#x27;创建时间&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) <span class="keyword">USING</span> BTREE</span><br><span class="line">) ENGINE = InnoDB CHARACTER <span class="built_in">SET</span> = utf8 COLLATE = utf8_general_ci ROW_FORMAT = Dynamic;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">INSERT INTO `t_sale_rank` VALUES (<span class="number">1</span>,  <span class="string">&#x27;0202&#x27;</span>, <span class="number">3535.60</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;2020-08-05 23:00:03&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">INSERT INTO `t_sale_rank` VALUES (<span class="number">2</span>,  <span class="string">&#x27;0207&#x27;</span>,<span class="number">12335.85</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;2020-08-05 23:00:03&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">INSERT INTO `t_sale_rank` VALUES (<span class="number">3</span>,  <span class="string">&#x27;0230&#x27;</span>, <span class="number">6727.20</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;2020-08-05 23:00:03&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">INSERT INTO `t_sale_rank` VALUES (<span class="number">4</span>,  <span class="string">&#x27;0234&#x27;</span>, <span class="number">3473.60</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;2020-08-05 23:00:03&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">INSERT INTO `t_sale_rank` VALUES (<span class="number">5</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;0256&#x27;</span>, <span class="number">8314.60</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;2020-08-05 23:00:03&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">INSERT INTO `t_sale_rank` VALUES (<span class="number">6</span>,  <span class="string">&#x27;0259&#x27;</span>,  <span class="number">4029.50</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;2020-08-05 23:00:03&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">INSERT INTO `t_sale_rank` VALUES (<span class="number">7</span>,  <span class="string">&#x27;0275&#x27;</span>, <span class="number">8147.50</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;2020-08-05 23:00:03&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">INSERT INTO `t_sale_rank` VALUES (<span class="number">8</span>,  <span class="string">&#x27;0276&#x27;</span>, <span class="number">3473.60</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;2020-08-05 23:00:03&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">INSERT INTO `t_sale_rank` VALUES (<span class="number">9</span>,  <span class="string">&#x27;0281&#x27;</span>,  <span class="number">1617.00</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;2020-08-05 23:00:03&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">INSERT INTO `t_sale_rank` VALUES (<span class="number">10</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;0298&#x27;</span>, <span class="number">3535.60</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;2020-08-05 23:00:03&#x27;</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><p>常见的排名分两种，一种是分数相同就按照提交分数的时间排名，另一种是分数相同排名就一样。</p><p><strong>1.排名不重复</strong></p><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">SELECT</span></span><br><span class="line">    a.*,@rank := @rank + <span class="number">1</span> AS rank</span><br><span class="line">FROM</span><br><span class="line">(</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">SELECT</span> id,emp_no,sale_amt,create_time FROM t_sale_rank <span class="built_in">GROUP</span> BY emp_no ORDER BY sale_amt DESC</span><br><span class="line">)a,(<span class="built_in">SELECT</span> @rank :=<span class="number">0</span>) b</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>结果：</p><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">+----+--------+----------+---------------------+------+</span><br><span class="line">| id | emp_no | sale_amt | create_time         | rank |</span><br><span class="line">+----+--------+----------+---------------------+------+</span><br><span class="line">|  <span class="number">2</span> | <span class="number">0207</span>   | <span class="number">12335.85</span> | <span class="number">2020</span><span class="literal">-08</span><span class="literal">-05</span> <span class="number">23</span>:<span class="number">00</span>:<span class="number">03</span> |    <span class="number">1</span> |</span><br><span class="line">|  <span class="number">5</span> | <span class="number">0256</span>   |  <span class="number">8314.60</span> | <span class="number">2020</span><span class="literal">-08</span><span class="literal">-05</span> <span class="number">23</span>:<span class="number">00</span>:<span class="number">03</span> |    <span class="number">2</span> |</span><br><span class="line">|  <span class="number">7</span> | <span class="number">0275</span>   |  <span class="number">8147.50</span> | <span class="number">2020</span><span class="literal">-08</span><span class="literal">-05</span> <span class="number">23</span>:<span class="number">00</span>:<span class="number">03</span> |    <span class="number">3</span> |</span><br><span class="line">|  <span class="number">3</span> | <span class="number">0230</span>   |  <span class="number">6727.20</span> | <span class="number">2020</span><span class="literal">-08</span><span class="literal">-05</span> <span class="number">23</span>:<span class="number">00</span>:<span class="number">03</span> |    <span class="number">4</span> |</span><br><span class="line">|  <span class="number">6</span> | <span class="number">0259</span>   |  <span class="number">4029.50</span> | <span class="number">2020</span><span class="literal">-08</span><span class="literal">-05</span> <span class="number">23</span>:<span class="number">00</span>:<span class="number">03</span> |    <span class="number">5</span> |</span><br><span class="line">| <span class="number">10</span> | <span class="number">0298</span>   |  <span class="number">3535.60</span> | <span class="number">2020</span><span class="literal">-08</span><span class="literal">-05</span> <span class="number">23</span>:<span class="number">00</span>:<span class="number">03</span> |    <span class="number">6</span> |</span><br><span class="line">|  <span class="number">1</span> | <span class="number">0202</span>   |  <span class="number">3535.60</span> | <span class="number">2020</span><span class="literal">-08</span><span class="literal">-05</span> <span class="number">23</span>:<span class="number">00</span>:<span class="number">03</span> |    <span class="number">7</span> |</span><br><span class="line">|  <span class="number">8</span> | <span class="number">0276</span>   |  <span class="number">3473.60</span> | <span class="number">2020</span><span class="literal">-08</span><span class="literal">-05</span> <span class="number">23</span>:<span class="number">00</span>:<span class="number">03</span> |    <span class="number">8</span> |</span><br><span class="line">|  <span class="number">4</span> | <span class="number">0234</span>   |  <span class="number">3473.60</span> | <span class="number">2020</span><span class="literal">-08</span><span class="literal">-05</span> <span class="number">23</span>:<span class="number">00</span>:<span class="number">03</span> |    <span class="number">9</span> |</span><br><span class="line">|  <span class="number">9</span> | <span class="number">0281</span>   |  <span class="number">1617.00</span> | <span class="number">2020</span><span class="literal">-08</span><span class="literal">-05</span> <span class="number">23</span>:<span class="number">00</span>:<span class="number">03</span> |   <span class="number">10</span> |</span><br><span class="line">+----+--------+----------+---------------------+------+</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>2.排名重复</strong></p><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">SELECT</span></span><br><span class="line">    a.*,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">IF</span>(@saleAmt = sale_amt,@rank,@rank := @temRank) AS rank,</span><br><span class="line">        (@temRank := @temRank + <span class="number">1</span> )AS temRank,</span><br><span class="line">        (@saleAmt := sale_amt) AS salement</span><br><span class="line">FROM</span><br><span class="line">(</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">SELECT</span> id,emp_no,sale_amt,create_time FROM t_sale_rank <span class="built_in">GROUP</span> BY emp_no ORDER BY sale_amt DESC</span><br><span class="line">)a,(<span class="built_in">SELECT</span> @rank :=<span class="number">1</span>, @temRank :=<span class="number">1</span>,@saleAmt :=<span class="number">0</span>) b</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">+----+--------+----------+---------------------+------+---------+----------+</span><br><span class="line">| id | emp_no | sale_amt | create_time         | rank | temRank | salement |</span><br><span class="line">+----+--------+----------+---------------------+------+---------+----------+</span><br><span class="line">|  <span class="number">2</span> | <span class="number">0207</span>   | <span class="number">12335.85</span> | <span class="number">2020</span><span class="literal">-08</span><span class="literal">-05</span> <span class="number">23</span>:<span class="number">00</span>:<span class="number">03</span> |    <span class="number">1</span> |       <span class="number">2</span> | <span class="number">12335.85</span> |</span><br><span class="line">|  <span class="number">5</span> | <span class="number">0256</span>   |  <span class="number">8314.60</span> | <span class="number">2020</span><span class="literal">-08</span><span class="literal">-05</span> <span class="number">23</span>:<span class="number">00</span>:<span class="number">03</span> |    <span class="number">2</span> |       <span class="number">3</span> |  <span class="number">8314.60</span> |</span><br><span class="line">|  <span class="number">7</span> | <span class="number">0275</span>   |  <span class="number">8147.50</span> | <span class="number">2020</span><span class="literal">-08</span><span class="literal">-05</span> <span class="number">23</span>:<span class="number">00</span>:<span class="number">03</span> |    <span class="number">3</span> |       <span class="number">4</span> |  <span class="number">8147.50</span> |</span><br><span class="line">|  <span class="number">3</span> | <span class="number">0230</span>   |  <span class="number">6727.20</span> | <span class="number">2020</span><span class="literal">-08</span><span class="literal">-05</span> <span class="number">23</span>:<span class="number">00</span>:<span class="number">03</span> |    <span class="number">4</span> |       <span class="number">5</span> |  <span class="number">6727.20</span> |</span><br><span class="line">|  <span class="number">6</span> | <span class="number">0259</span>   |  <span class="number">4029.50</span> | <span class="number">2020</span><span class="literal">-08</span><span class="literal">-05</span> <span class="number">23</span>:<span class="number">00</span>:<span class="number">03</span> |    <span class="number">5</span> |       <span class="number">6</span> |  <span class="number">4029.50</span> |</span><br><span class="line">| <span class="number">10</span> | <span class="number">0298</span>   |  <span class="number">3535.60</span> | <span class="number">2020</span><span class="literal">-08</span><span class="literal">-05</span> <span class="number">23</span>:<span class="number">00</span>:<span class="number">03</span> |    <span class="number">6</span> |       <span class="number">7</span> |  <span class="number">3535.60</span> |</span><br><span class="line">|  <span class="number">1</span> | <span class="number">0202</span>   |  <span class="number">3535.60</span> | <span class="number">2020</span><span class="literal">-08</span><span class="literal">-05</span> <span class="number">23</span>:<span class="number">00</span>:<span class="number">03</span> |    <span class="number">6</span> |       <span class="number">8</span> |  <span class="number">3535.60</span> |</span><br><span class="line">|  <span class="number">8</span> | <span class="number">0276</span>   |  <span class="number">3473.60</span> | <span class="number">2020</span><span class="literal">-08</span><span class="literal">-05</span> <span class="number">23</span>:<span class="number">00</span>:<span class="number">03</span> |    <span class="number">8</span> |       <span class="number">9</span> |  <span class="number">3473.60</span> |</span><br><span class="line">|  <span class="number">4</span> | <span class="number">0234</span>   |  <span class="number">3473.60</span> | <span class="number">2020</span><span class="literal">-08</span><span class="literal">-05</span> <span class="number">23</span>:<span class="number">00</span>:<span class="number">03</span> |    <span class="number">8</span> |      <span class="number">10</span> |  <span class="number">3473.60</span> |</span><br><span class="line">|  <span class="number">9</span> | <span class="number">0281</span>   |  <span class="number">1617.00</span> | <span class="number">2020</span><span class="literal">-08</span><span class="literal">-05</span> <span class="number">23</span>:<span class="number">00</span>:<span class="number">03</span> |   <span class="number">10</span> |      <span class="number">11</span> |  <span class="number">1617.00</span> |</span><br><span class="line">+----+--------+----------+---------------------+------+---------+----------+</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><p><strong>可能会出现以下的错误：</strong></p><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="number">1055</span> - Expression <span class="comment">#1 of SELECT list is not in GROUP BY clause and contains nonaggregated column &#x27;demo.t_sale_rank.id&#x27; which is not functionally dependent on columns in GROUP BY clause; this is incompatible with sql_mode=only_full_group_by</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>出现的原因：</strong></p><pre><code>MySQL 5.7.5及以上功能依赖检测功能。如果启用了ONLY_FULL_GROUP_BY SQL模式（默认情况下），MySQL将拒绝选择列表，HAVING条件或ORDER BY列表的查询引用在GROUP BY子句中既未命名的非集合列，也不在功能上依赖于它们。（5.7.5之前，MySQL没有检测到功能依赖关系，默认情况下不启用ONLY_FULL_GROUP_BY。有关5.7.5之前的行为的说明，请参见“MySQL5.6参考手册”。）</code></pre><p><strong>解决办法：</strong></p><p>方法一：</p><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mysql&gt; <span class="built_in">select</span> <span class="selector-tag">@</span>@global.sql_mode;</span><br><span class="line">+----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+</span><br><span class="line">| <span class="selector-tag">@</span>@global.sql_mode                                                                                           |</span><br><span class="line">+----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+</span><br><span class="line">|ONLY_FULL_GROUP_BY,STRICT_TRANS_TABLES,NO_ZERO_IN_DATE,NO_ZERO_DATE,ERROR_FOR_DIVISION_BY_ZERO,NO_AUTO_CREATE_USER,NO_ENGINE_SUBSTITUTION                                                                               |</span><br><span class="line">+----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+</span><br><span class="line">mysql&gt; <span class="built_in">set</span> <span class="selector-tag">@</span>@global.sql_mode=<span class="string">&#x27;STRICT_TRANS_TABLES,NO_ZERO_IN_DATE,NO_ZERO_DATE,ERROR_FOR_DIVISION_BY_ZERO,NO_AUTO_CREATE_USER,NO_ENGINE_SUBSTITUTION&#x27;</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>方法二：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">在MySQL安装路径下，找到my.ini配置文件,将文件中[mysqld]下，追加sql_mode&#x3D;STRICT_TRANS_TABLES,NO_ZERO_IN_DATE,NO_ZERO_DATE,ERROR_FOR_DIVISION_BY_ZERO,NO_AUTO_CREATE_USER,NO_ENGINE_SUBSTITUTION</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
